############################################################
#
#  ILDConfig - package for ilcsoft configuration files
#  such as Marlin steering files, gear geometry files,...
#  related to ILD (or CLIC_ILD)
#
#  01/2012
#  F.Gaede, DESY
############################################################

This new package just combines the old packages StandardConfig and MokkaDBConfig,
which will be obsolete form  release v01-13-03.


The configuration files in this release should work with the following Mokka models:
  ILD_o1_v05
  ILD_o2_v05
  ILD_o3_v05



subdirectories:

 StandardConfig/
 ----------------
    current
    -------
    current example files for running Mokka and Marlin
    (see: ./current/README for mini howto on using (this version of) ilcsoft )
     
    
    mc2008
    ------
    configuration files for 2008 Monte Carlo production for LOI
    
    
    clic_cdr
    ------
    configuration files for CLIC CDR production (2011)


 MokkaDBConfig/
 -------------

    current dump of the Mokka DB: mokka-dbdump.sql.tgz

    
    scripts
    -------
    scripts for related to running Mokka or the Mokka DB 


 LCFIPlusConfig/
 ---------------
    input files for flavor tagging

    steer
    -----
    example steering files

    vtxprob
    -------
    input histograms used for flavor tagging

    lcfiweights
    -----------
    TMVA weight files


 versions:
 ========

 - ./StandardConfig/lcgeo_current/
    - bbudsc_3evt_stdreco_dd4hep.xml
      - Fix the calorimeters collection name order in stringVec for input and output.
      - Fix forward calorimeter collection name, updated 'LHcalCollection' to 'LHCalCollection'.
      - Added one 'MyDDPandoraPFANewProcessor' configuration.
      - Added 'DDCaloDigi' Marlin processor, to use 'DDCaloDigi' for standard reconstruction within DD4hep/lcgeo framework.

    - Update the PandoraPFA steering files according to the current development of PhotonReconstructionAlgorithm in PandoraPFA. We copy the following new steering files from 'https://github.com/PandoraPFA/MarlinPandora/tree/master/scripts.
      - PandoraSettings_README.txt
      - PandoraSettingsPhotonTraining.xml
      - PandoraSettingsDefault.xml
      - PandoraLikelihoodData9EBin.xml
      - PandoraLikelihoodData1EBin.xml


 ------------
| v01-14-p00 |
 ------------

    - added new mokka dump: mokka-08-00-dbdump.sql.tgz (2012-06-19 - 16:38:53)
    - updated GearOutput.xml for ILD_o1_v05 and mokka-08-00
    - added /Mokka/init/mcRunNumber and 
      /Mokka/init/primaryVertexSpreadZ 0.300 mm to Mokka steering file
    - adapted grid job.sh script to use mcRunNumber

    - updated standard reconstruction (bbudsc_3evt_stdreco.xml):
      - turn on UseIterativeFitting for TruthTracker
      - merged in new calibration constants form J.Marshall (branch ucam_2012)
      - added new pandora settings: PandoraSettingsMuon.xml
      - use TruthTracker instead of SiliconTracking/FullLDCTracking for now
        (toggle with booleans in condition tag <if/> )
      - switched Pandora to not use TrackState @ Calorimeter for now
       ( UseOldTrackStateCalculation == 1 ) 
      - keep BuildUpVertex_RP and PrimaryVertex_RP collections on DST

